Use the following jQuery code to toggle the visibility of a table row:

```javascript
$(document).ready(function(){
  $(".toggler").click(function(){
    if($('.cat').css('display') === 'none'){
      $('.cat').css('display', 'block');
    }else{
      $('.cat').css('display', 'none');
    }  
  });
});
```

This script toggles the display of the element with class "cat" when the button with class "toggler" is clicked.

